<plot>15 years after a ranch house was half burned to the ground during a border dispute, a rancher and his daughter continue to relive the disappointment and anger of that day. With the daughter's discovery of a mysterious man swinging a large hammer against an outcropping of stone in the mountains on their land, events begin to unravel that lead to the moving conclusion of the film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?016536</url></doc>
